Package com.sportradar.livedata.sdk.proto.common

Interface RequestProducerListener<T extends OutgoingMessage>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the requests produced by the current RequestProducer
public interface RequestProducerListener<T extends OutgoingMessage>
Represents a listener used to observe the RequestProducer instances.
Author:
uros.bregar

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    boolean onRequestReady​(T request, boolean blocking)
    Invoked by the observed RequestProducer when a request for the betradar server is ready.

  • Method Details

    • onRequestReady

      boolean onRequestReady​(T request, boolean blocking)
      Invoked by the observed RequestProducer when a request for the betradar server is ready.
      Parameters:
      request - the OutgoingMessage derived type representing the request for the betradar server.
      blocking - true if request must be blocking.
      Returns:
      true if success.
